<!-- ABOUT US LANDING -->

<div class="jumbotron mb-0 text-center">
    <h1 class="display-4">Welcome to Photo Walks Colombia</h1>
    <p class="lead">The best resource for the best photo walks Colombia has to offer.</p>
    <hr class="my-4">
    <div class="row justify-content-center">
        <p class="col-lg-8">Photo Walks Colombia is an initiative born from the passion about photography and our interest in improving travel experiences. During our photo walks, out tour guide will take you and your fellow enthusiasts on a journey to experience and capture some of the most vibrant and picturesque locations in Colombia. Anyone interested in the art of taking pictures is welcome, we are always open to improving your skills and providing cultural tips to enhance your experience. We provide photography insights in a cultural and travel ambience so our customers can improve their skills to accomplish unique photographs while enjoying vibrant destinations.</p>
    </div>
    <a class="btn btn-success btn-lg" href="/about" role="button">Learn more!</a>
</div>

